'''Renatta Racing Systems''' was a ship-manufacturing company that existed during the latter years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. They were best known as the creators of the [[Renatta Needle Ship]], one of the fastest models of its type in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. However, because of the complexity and high costs associated with these ships (not to mention the inclusion of rare and dangerous components, such as [[Tobal lens]]es for the ships' [[photon drive system]]s), the company went bankrupt.

